no-empty-static-block.description:
Description

This rule disallows empty static blocks. This rule ignores static blocks which contain a comment.

Examples ofincorrectcode for this rule:

/*eslint no-empty-static-block: "error"*/

class Foo {
    static {}
}

Examples ofcorrectcode for this rule:

/*eslint no-empty-static-block: "error"*/

class Foo {
    static {
        bar();
    }
}

class Bar {
    static {
        // comment
    }
}
